          .support-section__bottom-text.font-s-22 по открытию ARETA FLOWERS
          form.support-section__form(data-feedback-form)
            input.input.support-item(type="text" name="name" autocomplete="off" placeholder="Имя")
            input.input.support-item(type="tel" name="phone" autocomplete="off" data-inputmask="'mask': '+7 (999) 999 9999'" placeholder="Телефон")
            button.btn.support-item-btn(type="submit") Получить План
